profile:
KAELEY is a multi-disciplinary firm; the integration of architectural, structural, mechanical and electrical services under one roof has enabled us to provide greater quality control to our projects. Quality control and sound training of personnel are our top management policies. Our company policy has been, and will continue to be, to provide consistent top quality professional services.
